import { Box, TextField, MenuItem, FormControl } from "@mui/material";

const Register = () => {
  return (
    <Box sx={{ display: "flex", flexWrap: "wrap", width: 500 }}>
      Register
      <Box>
        <FormControl>
          <TextField label="Email" variant="outlined" />
        </FormControl>
        <FormControl>
          <TextField label="Parolă" variant="outlined" />
        </FormControl>
        <FormControl>
          <TextField label="Confirmare parolă" variant="outlined" />
        </FormControl>
        <FormControl>
          <TextField label="Sex" variant="outlined" select sx={{ width: 75 }}>
            <MenuItem value=""></MenuItem>
            <MenuItem value="m">M</MenuItem>
            <MenuItem value="f">F</MenuItem>
          </TextField>
        </FormControl>
      </Box>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Register;
